---
import Container from "./ui/Container.astro";
import Link from "./ui/Link.astro";
---

<section id="authors-guidelines">
  <Container>
    <h1
      class="text-left text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-5xl mb-8"
    >
      Note:
    </h1>

    <ul
      class="divide-y divide-gray-200 dark:divide-gray-700 list-disc list-inside"
    >
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        It is mandatory that one author of an accepted paper has to made
        registration in order to make the paper to be appear in Technical
        Program and be included in the Conference Proceedings.
      </li>
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        Registration fee of a paper will be decided on the basis of the country
        of the first author's affiliation.
      </li>
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        There are no other charges from our side. Bank transaction charges will
        be applicable in addition to the registration fee.
      </li>
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        To avoid wastage of time, only one author will be allowed to present the
        paper and the presenter will be entitled to receive certificate of
        presentation. All other authors of the paper may attend the online
        presentation session without any extra charges and certificates provided
        to all.
      </li>
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        The authors are suggested to check their credentials before paying the
        registration fee and save the bank payment receipt.
      </li>
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        After paying registration fee, the bank payment receipt is required to
        be submitted within two days of the payment through a Google Form. Link
        will be provided through Email after acceptance of paper.
      </li>
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        Registration fee must be paid by wire transfer/online mode. Cash/demand
        draft/cheque will not be accepted.
      </li>
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        The authors are required to mention the Paper ID in the purpose or
        remark field while doing payment.
      </li>
      <li class="py-2 sm:py-3">
        The request of refunding the registration fee will not be considered in
        any case.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h1
      class="text-center text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-5xl my-8"
    >
      Call For Reviewers
    </h1>

    <p class="my-8">
      Faculty members, researchers, and industry professionals interested in
      joining as reviewers are invited to fill out the following <Link
        href="https://forms.gle/KdiGjhSo7s9WkLyS9">Google Form</Link
      >. Eligibility for reviewers requires either a completed or ongoing Ph.D.
      Each reviewer will be awarded a Certificate of Reviewer.
    </p>
  </Container>
</section>
